{
  "message": "revert: remove incompatible metamorphic cases (schema mismatch)\n\nThe added ufunc and linalg metamorphic cases used field schemas\nincompatible with the existing test harness. Reverting until\nharness can be updated to support new relation types.\n\nRemoved relations (to be re-added with harness support):\n- add_associative, mul_associative, mul_distributive\n- double_negation, add_identity, mul_identity\n- sub_self_zero, div_self_one\n- sum_transpose_invariant, prod_transpose_invariant\n- sum_concat_decomposition\n- inv_matmul_identity, det_transpose_invariant\n- svd_repeat_deterministic, eig_trace_sum, matrix_power_square\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
